{"tid":729131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"fb打錯字遭批誤人子弟　教育局長楊潤雄刪文後致歉","createTime":"2018-07-04T09:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T18:22:14.000Z","uid":39464,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"bf8c0d13e770ebae5950cb2f62053715d87c5cdf","tid":729131,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:51:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180704/s00001/ee8c842cfb490343c9a3e53799e13d1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180704%2Fs00001%2Fee8c842cfb490343c9a3e53799e13d1b.jpg&h=5df9c17f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥班子自上任以來，一直大打「親民牌」，不少司局長除了定期落區外，亦有開設社交媒體帳戶，希望展示線下線上全接觸的形象，不過「上得線多終遇苦」。<br />\n<br />\n政府新聞網上周六（6月30日）上載沙田百架無人機匯演慶回歸21周年的影片，教育局長楊潤雄昨日轉發有關的發文，不過竟然打錯字，將「值得推介」錯打成「藉得推介」，隨即被網民狠批，貴為教育局首長，竟然會在短短的發文中，出現錯別字，實為誤人子弟。<br />\n<br />\n局長其後知錯能改，刪去有關轉發的貼文後，再向公眾道歉：「多謝指正！昨晚在fb打錯字，多謝大家關心及提醒。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180704/s00001/1530697333386\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180704%2Fs00001%2F1530697333386&d=hcKOE3i8VJxvkOAuUfaprS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=c7c6a1c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180704%2Fs00001%2F1530697333386&h=db1b3f6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180704/s00001/1530697333386</a>"},{"pid":"e84c3d8911a9dae65a1d64aaae0efd99bcdc9c9c","tid":729131,"uid":41157,"like":31,"dislike":9,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:53:17.000Z","msg":"咁起碼佢都肯認錯"},{"pid":"6561363318d55ed014ecbeb897f4adbe69711780","tid":729131,"uid":99805,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:57:31.000Z","msg":"21th單野呢"},{"pid":"bf3b8f10bf8a7037112ad0763e59cecfe842f90f","tid":729131,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"ci